Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.02,0:00:09.78,Default1,,0,0,0,,平凡的三年級小學生\N\N高町奈葉與命運意外邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.86,0:00:15.11,Default1,,0,0,0,,堅信旭日的勇氣　緊握魔法的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.20,0:00:22.91,Default1,,0,0,0,,我能夠理解　鋼鐵般的意志\N\N是難以動搖　也難以捨棄的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.37,0:00:27.46,Default1,,0,0,0,,這是最初亦是最後的全力一戰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.04,0:00:30.26,Default1,,0,0,0,,我將以自己全部的魔法來回應
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.51,0:00:35.01,Default1,,0,0,0,,我願以千百次的呼喚　換得你的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.80,0:00:40.18,Default1,,0,0,0,,魔法少女奈葉　要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:36.30,Default1,,0,0,0,,母親…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:38.47,Default1,,0,0,0,,我的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.47,0:02:42.22,Default1,,0,0,0,,母親總是那樣的慈祥…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.85,0:02:45.85,Default1,,0,0,0,,總是親切地呼喚我的名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.10,0:02:49.56,Default1,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣　很漂亮吧？　艾麗茜婭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.73,0:02:51.44,Default1,,0,0,0,,艾麗茜婭？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.15,0:02:53.23,Default1,,0,0,0,,不對啊　媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:54.94,Default1,,0,0,0,,我是菲特啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:02:58.65,Default1,,0,0,0,,來　過來吧　艾麗茜婭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.95,0:03:09.58,Default1,,0,0,0,,嗯　真可愛　艾麗茜婭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.22,0:03:24.22,Default1,,0,0,0,,算了　沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:36.23,Default1,,0,0,0,,我深愛著慈祥的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:46.95,Default1,,0,0,0,,第十一話\N\N「時光彼岸的追憶」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.83,0:03:52.79,Default1,,0,0,0,,戰鬥開始了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:56.42,Default1,,0,0,0,,不過　難以置信呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:04:00.67,Default1,,0,0,0,,克洛諾君居然批准這種賭局
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:05.09,Default1,,0,0,0,,嗯　奈葉能贏當然最好不過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:10.27,Default1,,0,0,0,,但戰鬥結果其實無關緊要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:15.48,Default1,,0,0,0,,利用奈葉為我們爭取到的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.77,0:04:18.61,Default1,,0,0,0,,我們做好追蹤菲特的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.11,0:04:19.53,Default1,,0,0,0,,是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:23.74,Default1,,0,0,0,,成敗就全靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:25.07,Default1,,0,0,0,,可別讓她逃掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.49,0:04:27.99,Default1,,0,0,0,,嗯　就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.66,0:04:30.16,Default1,,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:41.01,Default1,,0,0,0,,但不將普蕾茜亞{\fnsimhei}·{\r}泰斯塔羅莎的\N\N家庭與事故詳情轉告奈葉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.97,0:04:47.30,Default1,,0,0,0,,我還是希望奈葉能取勝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:50.77,Default1,,0,0,0,,所以現在不要增加她的迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.86,0:05:04.99,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\t(\bord4\3c&H00BBBB&)}Photon Lancer{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}光子靈槍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.95,0:05:14.79,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fad(75,300)\t(0,1000,1,\bord4\3c&H8000BB&)}Divine Shooter{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}天神靈彈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.09,0:05:22.59,Default1,,0,0,0,,發射！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:24.84,Default1,,0,0,0,,發射！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:36.77,Default1,,0,0,0,,發射！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:39.94,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)}Scythe Form{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}光鐮形態
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.07,0:05:50.87,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)d\t(0,1500,1,\bord4\3c&H8000BB&)}Round Shield{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}魔力環盾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:18.23,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\t(\bord4\3c&H8000BB&)}Flash Move{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}瞬速移動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:37.04,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,0)\t(\bord4\3c&H00BBBB&)}Scythe Slash{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}光鐮裂斬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:46.84,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)}Fire{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}發射
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.56,0:07:07.78,Default1,,0,0,0,,起初她只是個魔力高強的外行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.69,0:07:09.40,Default1,,0,0,0,,但現在不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:11.53,Default1,,0,0,0,,出招既快又狠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:15.08,Default1,,0,0,0,,稍有遲疑　輸的人便是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.76,0:07:32.89,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\t(\bord4\3c&H800BBBB&)}Phalanx Shift{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}狂雷軍威
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.81,0:07:46.32,Default1,,0,0,0,,{\t(\bord4\3c&H800BBBB&)}雷光枷鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:48.53,Default1,,0,0,0,,不好　菲特是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.86,0:07:50.40,Default1,,0,0,0,,奈葉　我這就去幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.83,0:07:52.03,Default1,,0,0,0,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:56.70,Default1,,0,0,0,,艾爾芙和尤諾君都不要出手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:08:00.00,Default1,,0,0,0,,這是一對一的全力決鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:02.87,Default1,,0,0,0,,是屬於我與菲特的決鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:06.25,Default1,,0,0,0,,可是　菲特的這一招真的很危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.67,0:08:07.34,Default1,,0,0,0,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.63,0:08:10.38,Default1,,0,0,0,,阿爾卡斯　克洛塔斯　艾吉亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.51,0:08:12.84,Default1,,0,0,0,,疾風的天神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:15.26,Default1,,0,0,0,,遵從召喚奔騰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:17.51,Default1,,0,0,0,,巴勒基爾　紮魯哥爾　布洛澤爾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.14,0:08:24.15,Default1,,0,0,0,,{\t(\bord4\3c&H800BBBB&)}光子靈槍{\fnSimHei}·{\fnYouYuan}狂雷軍威
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:29.48,Default1,,0,0,0,,馳騁吧！　發射！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:49.38,Default1,,0,0,0,,奈葉！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.74,0:08:50.59,Default1,,0,0,0,,菲特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:25.54,Default1,,0,0,0,,攻擊結束後　枷鎖也就解開了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:28.21,Default1,,0,0,0,,現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.79,0:09:29.88,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\t(0,700,1,\bord4\3c&H8000BB&)}Divine──{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}天神──
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:32.96,Default1,,0,0,0,,輪到我了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.76,0:09:34.51,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\3c&H8000BB&}Buster{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}──烈破
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:49.48,Default1,,0,0,0,,直擊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:51.73,Default1,,0,0,0,,必須挺住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.61,0:09:54.53,Default1,,0,0,0,,不能輸給她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.59,0:10:19.30,Default1,,0,0,0,,菲特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:29.27,Default1,,0,0,0,,接我這招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:31.69,Default1,,0,0,0,,天神烈破的衍伸形態
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:37.53,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\t(0,1500,1,\bord4\3c&H8000BB&)}Starlight Breaker{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}星光聚裂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.96,0:10:48.83,Default1,,0,0,0,,枷鎖！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.79,0:10:53.84,Default1,,0,0,0,,這便是我的全力全開
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.17,0:10:59.43,Default1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1500)\t(1200,2400,1,\bord4\3c&H8000BB&)}星光聚裂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:15.98,Default1,,0,0,0,,好…　好強的魔力…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:18.86,Default1,,0,0,0,,哇…　菲特還活著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:43.59,Default1,,0,0,0,,菲特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.62,0:12:09.41,Default1,,0,0,0,,你醒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:10.58,Default1,,0,0,0,,菲特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:13.87,Default1,,0,0,0,,對不起　你還好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.79,0:12:19.05,Default1,,0,0,0,,可以算我贏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:23.97,Default1,,0,0,0,,看來是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.84,0:12:26.76,Faqi,,0,0,0,,Put out{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}釋放
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.35,0:12:31.85,Default1,,0,0,0,,還能飛嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.69,0:12:39.57,Default1,,0,0,0,,好　奈葉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.03,0:12:41.28,Default1,,0,0,0,,先回收聖石之種
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.90,0:12:42.82,Default1,,0,0,0,,然後帶她…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:43.95,Default1,,0,0,0,,等等…　來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.32,0:12:44.82,Default1,,0,0,0,,哎…？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:51.08,Default1,,0,0,0,,菲特！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.17,0:13:02.51,Default1,,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:03.72,Default1,,0,0,0,,捕捉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.17,0:13:04.84,Default1,,0,0,0,,幹得好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:07.18,Default1,,0,0,0,,物質傳送是會輕易暴露自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.64,0:13:08.22,Default1,,0,0,0,,鎖定座標
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:10.51,Default1,,0,0,0,,已經鎖定　設定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.93,0:13:12.81,Default1,,0,0,0,,武裝局員
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:14.35,Default1,,0,0,0,,由傳送門出動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.52,0:13:18.52,Default1,,0,0,0,,立刻逮捕普蕾茜亞{\fnSimHei}·{\r}泰斯塔羅莎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.86,0:13:19.57,Default1,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:31.49,Default1,,0,0,0,,我的身體已承受不住次元魔法了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.45,0:13:33.25,Default1,,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:35.96,Default1,,0,0,0,,剛才的傳送已將位置暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.88,0:13:38.42,Default1,,0,0,0,,菲特…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:40.54,Default1,,0,0,0,,她還是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.96,0:13:44.67,Default1,,0,0,0,,是該啟程的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:16.75,Default1,,0,0,0,,第二小隊　傳送成功
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:18.83,Default1,,0,0,0,,第一小隊　開始侵入
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:21.88,Default1,,0,0,0,,辛苦你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:24.46,Default1,,0,0,0,,另外…　菲特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.01,0:14:25.76,Default1,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.72,0:14:38.10,Default1,,0,0,0,,不能讓她目睹母親被逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.56,0:14:41.11,Default1,,0,0,0,,奈葉　帶她去別的房間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:42.15,Default1,,0,0,0,,啊…　是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:43.94,Default1,,0,0,0,,菲特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.02,0:14:45.82,Default1,,0,0,0,,不如到我的房間去…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.19,0:14:48.99,Default1,,0,0,0,,全員　侵入中央殿堂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.32,0:14:50.16,Default1,,0,0,0,,發現目標
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:52.57,Default1,,0,0,0,,普蕾茜亞{\fnSimHei}·{\r}泰斯塔羅莎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:57.08,Default1,,0,0,0,,因違反時空管理法\N\N並攻擊管理局艦船
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:14:58.29,Default1,,0,0,0,,你被捕了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:15:00.62,Default1,,0,0,0,,解除武裝　到這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.26,0:15:12.09,Default1,,0,0,0,,守住那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.55,0:15:13.55,Default1,,0,0,0,,這裡有什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.10,0:15:17.22,Default1,,0,0,0,,這…　這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.13,0:15:52.43,Default1,,0,0,0,,不要靠近我的艾麗茜婭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.43,0:15:57.06,Default1,,0,0,0,,開火！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:03.52,Default1,,0,0,0,,真煩人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.52,0:16:07.82,Default1,,0,0,0,,危險！　快防禦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:24.46,Default1,,0,0,0,,不好　快送局員們返航！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:26.21,Default1,,0,0,0,,明…　明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.34,0:16:29.42,Default1,,0,0,0,,艾麗…　茜婭…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.01,0:16:32.30,Default1,,0,0,0,,座標鎖定　0120503
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.51,0:16:34.22,Default1,,0,0,0,,鎖定　傳送準備就緒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:45.23,Default1,,0,0,0,,已經不行了　我們沒有時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:52.11,Default1,,0,0,0,,僅靠9顆太古遺產\N\N不知能否到達「阿爾哈紮德」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.28,0:16:57.57,Default1,,0,0,0,,但已經足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.91,0:16:59.28,Default1,,0,0,0,,到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:03.62,Default1,,0,0,0,,不必再忍受失去女兒的悲痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:09.00,Default1,,0,0,0,,也不必再把人偶當作女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.17,0:17:13.30,Default1,,0,0,0,,聽見了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.84,0:17:16.01,Default1,,0,0,0,,我說的就是你　菲特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.64,0:17:19.64,Default1,,0,0,0,,我把艾麗茜婭的記憶給了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.65,0:17:21.77,Default1,,0,0,0,,但你卻只有外表像她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.22,0:17:27.52,Default1,,0,0,0,,根本就是個毫無用處的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:30.94,Default1,,0,0,0,,在最初的事故中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:36.74,Default1,,0,0,0,,普蕾茜亞失去了親生女兒\N\N艾麗茜婭{\fnsimhei}·{\r}泰斯塔羅莎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:40.24,Default1,,0,0,0,,她最後進行的研究
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.37,0:17:41.79,Default1,,0,0,0,,是不同於使役魔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:45.54,Default1,,0,0,0,,而又超越使役魔的人工生命技術
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:49.63,Default1,,0,0,0,,以及使死者復甦的秘術
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:55.92,Default1,,0,0,0,,「F.A.T.E」是她當時的\N\N研究的開發代號
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.09,0:17:58.80,Default1,,0,0,0,,你調查的真詳細啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.26,0:18:01.43,Default1,,0,0,0,,是啊　你說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.51,0:18:03.89,Default1,,0,0,0,,但是　不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.14,0:18:06.06,Default1,,0,0,0,,研究一點也不順利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:09.65,Default1,,0,0,0,,人工生命終歸是人工產物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.69,0:18:13.44,Default1,,0,0,0,,無法替代逝去的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.94,0:18:19.45,Default1,,0,0,0,,艾麗茜婭的笑容要更加燦爛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.07,0:18:26.20,Default1,,0,0,0,,艾麗茜婭儘管有時任性\N\N卻很是乖巧而聽話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.58,0:18:27.46,Default1,,0,0,0,,別說了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:32.21,Default1,,0,0,0,,與艾麗茜婭的每時每刻都充滿溫馨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:37.17,Default1,,0,0,0,,菲特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:41.05,Default1,,0,0,0,,你終究不過是艾麗茜婭的仿製品
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.60,0:18:46.52,Default1,,0,0,0,,枉費我給了你艾麗茜婭的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.18,0:18:48.06,Default1,,0,0,0,,別說了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.56,0:18:49.69,Default1,,0,0,0,,別再說了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.15,0:18:57.32,Default1,,0,0,0,,你只是艾麗茜婭復活前\N\N我用於安撫自己的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.49,0:19:00.74,Default1,,0,0,0,,所以我不再需要你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.24,0:19:03.45,Default1,,0,0,0,,快從我的眼前消失吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:07.41,Default1,,0,0,0,,求求你　不要再說了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:25.39,Default1,,0,0,0,,告訴你一件事吧　菲特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.89,0:19:28.68,Default1,,0,0,0,,自從造出你以來…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.77,0:19:32.60,Default1,,0,0,0,,我一直都非常非常厭惡你！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.87,0:19:45.62,Default1,,0,0,0,,菲特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.37,0:19:46.87,Default1,,0,0,0,,菲特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.95,0:19:50.00,Default1,,0,0,0,,已成功回收了局員們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.16,0:19:52.66,Default1,,0,0,0,,不…　不好了不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.67,0:19:53.83,Default1,,0,0,0,,快看這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.42,0:19:57.21,Default1,,0,0,0,,建築物內出現眾多魔力反應
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.25,0:19:57.80,Default1,,0,0,0,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.51,0:19:59.67,Default1,,0,0,0,,發生了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:31.20,Default1,,0,0,0,,庭院內出現魔力反應
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:32.62,Default1,,0,0,0,,個個都是A級
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:35.04,Default1,,0,0,0,,總數60…　80…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.21,0:20:35.96,Default1,,0,0,0,,還在繼續增加
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.17,0:20:37.38,Default1,,0,0,0,,普蕾茜亞{\fnSimHei}·{\r}泰斯塔羅莎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.04,0:20:39.50,Default1,,0,0,0,,你到底打算做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.57,0:21:04.95,Default1,,0,0,0,,我不希望我們的旅程遭人打擾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,0:21:11.12,Default1,,0,0,0,,我們就要啟程了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.25,0:21:21.51,Default1,,0,0,0,,去尋覓那遺失的聖都\N\N──「阿爾哈紮德」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.68,0:21:28.51,Default1,,0,0,0,,難道你要…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.22,0:21:30.97,Default1,,0,0,0,,我們要憑藉這力量啟程
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.72,0:21:33.52,Default1,,0,0,0,,去找回…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.18,0:21:35.27,Default1,,0,0,0,,失去的一切！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.69,0:21:41.53,Default1,,0,0,0,,是次元震！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.82,0:21:42.65,Default1,,0,0,0,,超過中級規模
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.03,0:21:44.11,Default1,,0,0,0,,採取抗震防禦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.36,0:21:45.70,Default1,,0,0,0,,展開異相屏障
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.15,0:21:48.03,Default1,,0,0,0,,9顆聖石之種發動
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.11,0:21:50.08,Default1,,0,0,0,,次元震的等級正在增加
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.49,0:21:52.33,Default1,,0,0,0,,保持傳送可能的距離
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.58,0:21:54.33,Default1,,0,0,0,,向影響較弱的空域移動
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.60,0:21:55.75,Default1,,0,0,0,,明…　明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.08,0:21:57.17,Default1,,0,0,0,,亂次係數擴大
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.62,0:21:59.17,Default1,,0,0,0,,這樣下去將引發次元斷層
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.09,0:22:03.51,Default1,,0,0,0,,阿爾…　哈紮德…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.71,0:22:04.80,Default1,,0,0,0,,太荒謬了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.76,0:22:06.55,Default1,,0,0,0,,克洛諾君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.26,0:22:08.26,Default1,,0,0,0,,我去阻止她
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.55,0:22:09.39,Default1,,0,0,0,,打開傳送門
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.85,0:22:16.06,Default1,,0,0,0,,遺失的聖都　阿爾哈紮德
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.89,0:22:19.73,Default1,,0,0,0,,失落的禁斷秘術所沉睡的土地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.56,0:22:22.57,Default1,,0,0,0,,你打算去那裡做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.98,0:22:26.53,Default1,,0,0,0,,你以為能找回流逝的過去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.16,0:22:38.67,Default1,,0,0,0,,無論使用怎樣的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.08,0:22:42.09,Default1,,0,0,0,,都不可能重新找回過去！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.65,0:23:14.08,Default1,,0,0,0,,我與艾麗茜婭將在阿爾哈紮德\N\N挽回過去的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.57,0:25:14.32,Default1,,0,0,0,,被引發的次元震
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.82,0:25:18.32,Default1,,0,0,0,,為了阻止普蕾茜亞　我們闖入時光庭院
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.91,0:25:21.08,Default1,,0,0,0,,奈葉的世界　我們的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.83,0:25:23.83,Default1,,0,0,0,,為了不使眾多世界因此滅亡
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.71,0:25:26.46,Default1,,0,0,0,,這時　菲特又會怎樣抉擇？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.38,0:25:31.09,Default1,,0,0,0,,下集　魔法少女奈葉　第十二話
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.84,0:25:33.51,Default1,,0,0,0,,宿命終結的時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.63,0:25:37.68,Default1,,0,0,0,,莉莉卡露瑪姬卡露　我會堅持到最後
